					<msContents>
						<summary>

						<p>An inscription of the same year recording the improvement effected to a (temple) land for making it cultivable by one Kavarāmoḻi Mādēvaṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Toṇḍaraḍippoḍi. The yield from this land seems to have been intended to meet the expenses of worship of the (goddess) Bhaṭṭārakī.</p>						

						</summary>
